subTitle: In Japan, evil organizations battle superheroes for world domination. Miss Kuroitsu works for one such group, creating monsters to defeat a hero, while facing typical corporate challenges.

title: Anyone But You
subTitle: What begins as an instant attraction for Ben and Bea quickly takes a nosedive, culminating in a tense reunion at a wedding they both attend six months later.

title: Lake Placid: The Final Chapter
subTitle: Reba builds an electric fence to block all the crocodiles in Black Lake. But when the fence is unknowingly left open, some students trespass on the property, which puts their lives in danger.

title: Daddio
subTitle: A woman takes a cab ride back home from the airport. En route, she unexpectedly has an insightful conversation with the driver regarding the important relationships in life.

title: Alpha
subTitle: Keda, the young son of a tribe chief, is accidentally left behind, and must survive in the wilderness. He encounters an injured wolf abandoned by its pack, and the two form a bond.

subTitle: Peter Murdoch, a wealthy man, funds a project wherein two anacondas are tested in a research laboratory. Later, a mercenary is hired to stop the snakes after they escape and go on a killing spree.

subTitle: Determined to cure the disease that has plagued him his entire life, Morbius conducts a drastic experiment, which bears unforeseen consequences.

subTitle: Sebastian Caine, a scientist, develops an invisibility serum. However, when he uses it on himself and is unable to reverse the effects, it results in horrifying consequences.

title: Brightburn
subTitle: Tori and Kyle find a baby boy in a spaceship and adopt him as their own child, Brandon. However, after turning 12, Brandon learns that he has superpowers and begins to use them for sinister purposes.

subTitle: Agent M, a probationary member of the MIB, teams up with Agent H and uncovers a sinister plot that reveals a traitor in the organisation aiding an alien invasion.

subTitle: Peter Parker tries to stop the Vulture from selling weapons made with advanced Chitauri technology while trying to balance his life as an ordinary high school student.
